<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>درس رياضيات: العدد 1000</title>
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animejs/3.2.1/anime.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
    }
    .lesson-header {
      background-color: #fffacd;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .lesson-content {
      border: 2px solid #ff69b4;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff0f5;
    }
    .interactive {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .interactive:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #ffe4e1;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 5px;
    }
    .verify {
      background-color: #ffebcd;
      border: 2px solid #ff6347;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .speech-bubble {
      position: relative;
      background: #ffebcd;
      border-radius: .4em;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .speech-bubble:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 100%;
      left: 50%;
      border-width: 10px;
      border-style: solid;
      border-color: #ffebcd transparent transparent transparent;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lesson-header">
      <h1>الدرس 1: العدد 1000</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="lesson-content">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <div class="highlight">
            <p>سنتعلم مكونات العدد 1000 باستعمال (المئات)</p>
          </div>
          <img src="path/to/your/image_of_money.jpg" class="img-fluid interactive" alt="صورة النقود">
          <p>أدي تسع لوحات أضف لوحة مئة فتصبح لدي ألف</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <div class="row mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <img src="path/to/your/image_of_100_units.jpg" class="img-fluid interactive" alt="100 وحدة">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <p>+</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <img src="path/to/your/image_of_100_units.jpg" class="img-fluid interactive" alt="100 وحدة">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <p>=</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="highlight">
                <p>900</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <p>+</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="highlight">
                <p>100</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <p>= 1000</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="verify">
            <p>عد المئات، ثم اكتب العدد في الفراغ:</p>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="highlight">
                  <p>......</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="highlight">
                  <p>......</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="highlight">
                  <p>1000</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
              <img id="talking-child" src="path/to/your/child_image.jpg" class="img-fluid interactive" alt="صورة الطفل">
              <div id="speech-bubble" class="speech-bubble mt-2">
                <p>عد المئات، ثم اكتب العدد في الفراغ:</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
      var textElement = document.querySelector("#speech-bubble p");
      var text = textElement.textContent;
      textElement.textContent = "";
      anime({
        targets: textElement,
        textContent: [0, text.length],
        round: 1,
        easing: 'easeInOutQuad',
        duration: 3000,
        update: function(anim) {
          var progress = Math.round(anim.progress);
          textElement.textContent = text.substring(0, progress / 100 * text.length);
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
